1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:04,920
Hi and welcome to The Winning Factor. I'm Alan Aitken and on this show each week
大家好，歡迎收聽《致勝因素》。我是艾倫·艾特肯，本節目每週為您帶來……

2
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:10,260
we take a look at some upcoming races in Hong Kong, try to identify an angle to
我們將檢視香港即將舉行之賽事，嘗試找出切入點。

3
00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:15,120
the race that might lead us to finding the winner. Well it's Saturday racing
這場可能揭曉勝者的賽事，將於星期六進行。

4
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:19,820
this weekend in Hong Kong and the first race I'm going to take a look at is race
本週末於香港，首場賽事我將關注的是第幾場。

5
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:25,680
10 where our winning factor is the map. So this is class 3 1600 meters and
第十場，我們的致勝因素是地圖。此役為三級賽 1600 米，目前……

6
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:29,260
And Blazing Wukong and Amazing Partners are coming off last start wins.
「烈火悟空」與「驚奇拍檔」於上一場賽事勝出後，今仗再戰。

7
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:33,140
Endured has been racing well in similar events without much luck.
「Endured」在類似賽事中表現不俗，但始終未能取勝。

8
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:35,920
Smart Avenue should improve with a better draw.
智道有望憑藉更佳的起跑表現而提升。

9
00:00:36,380 --> 00:00:40,540
And Family Jewel and Hymnbook both look to have chances as well.
而「Family Jewel」與「Hymnbook」亦均具機會。

10
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:44,460
So not a one horse race by any means.
因此，這絕非一場單騎獨進的賽事。

11
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:45,560
Quite a few chances.
機會相當多。

12
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:53,920
But I'm looking most closely at a couple of horses I think will cope with what looks quite a tricky event in terms of the map.
不過我主要關注數匹馬，認為牠們應付這個看似頗具挑戰性的地圖賽事不成問題。

13
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:57,380
And that's Blazing Wukong and Amazing Partners.
此為《火雲猴王》與《驚奇夥伴》。

14
00:00:58,220 --> 00:01:01,540
Now, Amazing Partners, first of all, well, he's lightly raced.
現在，Amazing Partners，首先，其出賽次數較少。

15
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:03,880
He's only had six starts for three wins.
他至今僅出賽六場，取得三場勝利。

16
00:01:04,380 --> 00:01:08,440
And this was his latest when he tackled 1,600 metres for the first time.
這正是他首次挑戰一千六百公尺時的最後一役。

17
00:01:08,860 --> 00:01:12,200
This is race 601. He's in gate four pink colours.
此為第 601 場賽事，他位於四號閘，身穿粉紅色賽衣。

18
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:16,200
And Amazing Partners jumps well. He isn't a quick horse naturally.
Amazing Partners 跳躍能力出色，但天生並非速度型賽駒。

19
00:01:16,740 --> 00:01:20,280
But Vincent Ho is able to get him into a position near the lead
但何秉遠成功將其帶至接近領先位置。

20
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:22,960
through what is a slow first sectional
首節比賽節奏緩慢。

21
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:26,760
before the pace does pick up a little through the middle stages,
在賽段中段速度稍為提升之前，

22
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,920
but still is only steady.
但始終僅屬平穩。

23
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:32,100
A number of Saturday's rivals are here too.
本週六的若干對手亦已蒞臨。

24
00:01:32,260 --> 00:01:34,540
In Jude, inside amazing partners in red and grey,
朱德，令人驚嘆的紅灰配色馬匹。

25
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:37,760
Mr Dapper, the leader, and Himbuk in green near the tail.
達珀先生為領頭馬，身著綠色服裝的欣布克則位於尾部附近。

26
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:41,240
Now, the field is bunched here with no serious pace
現時賽場上馬羣聚集，未能展開有效步速。

27
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:44,040
and becomes just a dash down the straight,
並成為直道上的標誌點，

28
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,460
with in Jude on the inside having no luck.
猶德在內部毫無運氣。

29
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:49,280
But amazing partners, well, he's able to be challenging
但令人驚嘆的夥伴，他確實能帶來挑戰。

30
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,960
at the right time with enough turn of foot
在恰當時機展現足夠的靈巧步伐

31
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,760
to reel in the leaders and he grinds out the win.
他成功吸引領導層加入，並穩紮穩打贏得勝利。

32
00:01:56,300 --> 00:02:00,580
Now, despite his good winning record, three from six amazing partners,
現時，儘管其勝出率理想，且擁有三位從六場比賽中表現出色的搭檔，

33
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:03,580
I don't really think we've seen the best of him yet
我並不認為我們已見識到他最出色的一面。

34
00:02:03,580 --> 00:02:06,620
because he's been in several of these kinds of races
因其曾參加多次同類賽事。

35
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:09,460
where it's just a grinding sort of finish,
那是一種類似研磨的表面處理。

36
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,760
difficult to get separation on the field.
在場上難以取得分離效果。

37
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:15,220
So he's done well to put that record together
他成功籌組了該紀錄片。

38
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:19,620
and that could be a key thing in Saturday's race.
這或許是星期六賽事的一個關鍵因素。

39
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:21,220
Now, Blazing Wukong, on the other hand,
另一方面，現正進行的《烈焰悟空》。

40
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:26,340
He's a little bit more well explored with 11 starts so far for three wins.
他已較多出賽，至今十一場勝出三場。

41
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:28,160
And here's his latest offering.
此乃其最新推出之作。

42
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:29,980
This is race 643.
此為第 643 場賽事。
